WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.160
Do you know where I might find him?
The son?

00:00:02.353 --> 00:00:04.720
Next to his father at the cemetery.

00:00:04.913 --> 00:00:09.202
He was killed in an accident
on a construction site, years ago.

00:00:10.993 --> 00:00:12.597
But...

00:00:14.193 --> 00:00:16.514
...she might still be alive.
His widow.

00:00:17.433 --> 00:00:19.640
Do you know where
I might find her?

